    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Oh, Hel No!</strong> combines crafting, base-building, and horde survival in a wild journey of chicken-esque and demonic ambition. As a scrappy little imp banished to the surface, you’ve got one mission: prove yourself, survive waves of enemies, and conquer the trials of Hel to reclaim your throne.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with friends in the Overworld to gather resources, craft gear, level up skills, and build a killer base. Then, descend into Hel to face off in never-ending battles that’ll push you to the limit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/73fad283e9df029a621a38a7e7b56112.poster.avif?t=1750116547\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/73fad283e9df029a621a38a7e7b56112.webm?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/73fad283e9df029a621a38a7e7b56112.mp4?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD, CRAFT &amp; EXPLORE THE OVERWORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/2497aa6c12a6f8db69684f25176daca1.poster.avif?t=1750116547\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/2497aa6c12a6f8db69684f25176daca1.webm?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/2497aa6c12a6f8db69684f25176daca1.mp4?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Overworld is where you gather resources, upgrade gear, explore hidden activities, and build a base to keep you prepared. Craft epic armor, discover stat-boosting recipes, and set up workshops for your next journey into Hel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VENTURE INTO HEL, FIGHT, &amp; LEVEL UP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/9e9d245ab33a9bb88a4424a5d35d3314.poster.avif?t=1750116547\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/9e9d245ab33a9bb88a4424a5d35d3314.webm?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/9e9d245ab33a9bb88a4424a5d35d3314.mp4?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Entering Hel ain't gonna be easy, you need <strong>Infernal Keys</strong> crafted from rarest of Overworld resources (Just some rocks...). With each wave, enemies get stronger, so expand your gear and refine your materials to keep up! AND BRING EXTRAS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat waves of minions, earn XP, and unlock Talent Points to boost your combat and resource skills. How you play is up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BRING YOUR FRIENDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/3a29b47b4f6d791c9057c4807409a8fd.poster.avif?t=1750116547\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/3a29b47b4f6d791c9057c4807409a8fd.webm?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/3a29b47b4f6d791c9057c4807409a8fd.mp4?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up to build, battle, or just hang out and enjoy some in-game downtime... with Chickens if you want. Chickens are friends...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Loop</strong>: Gather, craft, battle, repeat! Prepare in the Overworld and face waves of enemies in Hel until you’re ready to take on the Champion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Base-Building &amp; Crafting</strong>: Set up workshops, cook for stat boosts, and keep resources flowing with a mix of strategy and chill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Horde Survival Combat</strong>: Face waves of enemies that only get tougher with each round!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Talent System</strong>: Level up and customize combat and resource perks to match your play style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overworld Shenanigans</strong>: Play mini-games, pet chickens, and explore while gearing up for the next big battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to rise and claim the throne? Let’s dive in!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Oh... and Chickens...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/4ad69174bcff3b5a1e92f7b13179c9e2.poster.avif?t=1750116547\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/4ad69174bcff3b5a1e92f7b13179c9e2.webm?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225370/extras/4ad69174bcff3b5a1e92f7b13179c9e2.mp4?t=1750116547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
